step.tex:
\begin{align}
\int \dfrac{x^3 - x^2 + x - 1 }{x - 1}\,dx &= \int \left(x^2 + 1\right)dx\\
												&= \int x^2dx + \int 1\,dx\\
												&= \dfrac{x^3}{3}  +x + C

\end{align}\\
\text{Here C is the constant of integration.}

